headline: Forget DRI Stock and Look at TXRH Instead

headline: Mizuho Sees Sales Upside at Darden (DRI), Flags Ongoing Commodity Cost Pressure
summary: Darden Restaurants, Inc. (NYSE:DRI) is included among the 13 Best January Dividend Stocks to Invest in. On December 22, Mizuho analyst Nick Setyan raised the firm’s price target on Darden Restaurants, Inc. (NYSE:DRI) to $195 from $185 and kept a Neutral rating on the shares. The firm updated its estimates after the company released earnings. […]
